  "texts": [
    "Human writers also use similar expressions and make different kinds of mistakes in their texts.",
    "However, it is essential to develop a literary taste, to be able to distinguish between a high-quality stylistic device that will beautify a piece of writing and artistic incompetence and even graphomania.",
    "This leads us to the necessity of a conscious approach and critical thinking development while using AI agents for creative writing.",
    "A mindful AI usage will help find inspiration in its answers, save time, and create valuable artwork that will be appreciated by human readers.",
    "The results of our research show that ChatGPT, as well as other AI-powered tools for text generation and transformation, can be quite useful in idea proposing, different parts of the story development and stylistic device refinement."
